'''斯圖爾特·阿姆斯特朗'''（{{lang-en|Stuart Armstrong}}；{{bd|1992年|3月30日}}）是一位[[蘇格蘭|蘇格蘭]]足球運動員。在場上的位置是中場。現在效力於[[英格兰足球超级联赛|英超]]球隊[[南安普顿足球俱乐部|南安普顿]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/31044217|title=Stuart Armstrong: Dundee United reject Celtic and Burnley bids|date=29 January 2015|accessdate=2 February 2015|author=Jim Spence|publisher=BBC Sport|archive-date=2015-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150201082135/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/31044217|dead-url=no}}</ref>，[[蘇格蘭足球代表隊|蘇格蘭足球代表隊]]成員，他也曾代表蘇格蘭各級國家青年足球隊參賽<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.scottishfa.co.uk/football_player_profile.cfm?page=105&playerID=51419&squadID=9 |title=SFA U19 profile |access-date=2015-06-05 |archive-date=2018-06-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180624041230/https://www.scottishfa.co.uk/players/?pid=51419&lid=9 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.scottishfa.co.uk/football_player_profile.cfm?page=105&playerID=51419&squadID=5 |title=SFA U21 profile |access-date=2015-06-05 |archive-date=2021-05-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210520073059/https://www.scottishfa.co.uk/players/?pid=51419&lid=5 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 俱樂部生涯 ==
=== 南安普顿 ===
阿姆斯特朗於2018年6月與[[南安普顿足球俱乐部|南安普顿]]簽署了一份為期四年的合約。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.celticfc.net/news/14535 |title=Stuart Armstrong signs for Southampton on a four-year deal |publisher=Celtic F.C. |date=26 June 2018 |accessdate=26 June 2018 |archive-date=2020-09-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200926063818/http://www.celticfc.net/news/14535 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Stuart Armstrong: Southampton sign Celtic midfielder on four-year deal |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/44619120 |publisher=BBC Sport |accessdate=26 June 2018 |date=26 June 2018 |archive-date=2021-08-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210804171347/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/44619120 |dead-url=no }}</ref>他說，他想在俱樂部“紮根”。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/44626200 |title=Stuart Armstrong: Southampton signing from Celtic aims to 'hit ground running' |date=27 June 2018 |accessdate=27 June 2018 |publisher=BBC Sport |archive-date=2021-08-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210804171309/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/44626200 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2021年1月1日，阿姆斯特朗宣布與南安普顿簽訂了新的三年半合約，合同期限將持續到2024年夏天。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.southamptonfc.com/news/2021-01-01/announcement-stuart-armstrong-new-southampton-contract-2024|title=New deal for Armstrong|date=2021-01-01|website=Southampton FC|access-date=2021-01-27|archive-date=2021-07-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210721222826/https://www.southamptonfc.com/news/2021-01-01/announcement-stuart-armstrong-new-southampton-contract-2024|dead-url=no}}</ref>

